Subject: RE: [T2] RE: [VB] Re: [T2] first drive single port dog house

Has to be 1300-1500 SP, otherwise the dog house fanshroud wouldn't fit width
wise. I have converted a number of SP SR engines over to dog house in the
past. Generally I would recommend getting a DR block with the bigger oil pump,
but the SR can be converted easily by dropping the parts right on.

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3
71 Trike 1776cc Dual T-4 34 PDSIT-3
VolksAir 1585cc 31 PICT
Ray, Kent WA
